Interface NCIntentSolver.Predicate

    public static interface NCIntentSolver.Predicate
extends Function<NCToken,org.apache.commons.lang3.tuple.Pair<Boolean,int[]>>
    Marker type of pattern items. Only built-in NCIntentSolver.OR, NCIntentSolver.AND, NCIntentSolver.NAND, NCIntentSolver.NOR, NCIntentSolver.XOR, NCIntentSolver.XNOR or NCIntentSolver.RULE implementations are supported, i.e. no user-defined implementation are allowed.
    See Also:
    RULE, OR, AND, NAND, XOR, XNOR, NOR
